27:53.380 --> 27:54.922
And that's how it got started.

27:56.633 --> 28:00.052
Carney: This isn't really
a typical criminal trial.

28:00.428 --> 28:04.390
James Bulger knows
that by following the strategy

28:04.516 --> 28:07.226
he has directed us to do,

28:07.435 --> 28:10.521
he will be found guilty,
