01:17:43.158 --> 01:17:46.952
Man: John wouldn't play ball
with the prosecutors.

01:17:47.120 --> 01:17:48.329
They then focused on John.

01:17:48.497 --> 01:17:51.457
"Oh, okay, you don't want to play
ball with us, we'll show you."

01:17:51.625 --> 01:17:53.542
And they then started
looking at John,

01:17:53.752 --> 01:17:55.628
and made a case against John.

01:17:56.254 --> 01:18:00.633
The government decided that the person
they really needed to get is Connolly,

01:18:00.842 --> 01:18:03.177
that's the case
they're trying to make.

01:18:03.428 --> 01:18:08.683
So John Martorano who had never met
John Connolly, never met him,

01:18:08.850 --> 01:18:13.229
goes to them and says, "l can link
John Connolly to the Wheeler murder.

01:18:13.438 --> 01:18:17.692
And l can link John Connolly
to the Callahan murder."

01:18:23.281 --> 01:18:27.451
Man: The defendant John Connolly,
he's just another member of the gang.

01:18:27.619 --> 01:18:30.413
They pay him money,
he gives them information.

01:18:30.622 --> 01:18:33.207
English: They arrive at the conclusion
